# Minesweeper Game Java Project

This project is a Java implementation of the classic Minesweeper game. It provides a graphical user interface (GUI) for players to interact with the game board and uncover mines without detonating them.

## Features

- **GUI Interface:** The game provides a user-friendly GUI for players to play Minesweeper.
- **Customizable Grid:** Players can choose the size of the grid and the number of mines to customize their game experience.
- **Timer:** The game includes a timer to track the player's progress.
- **Win/Loss Detection:** The game detects when a player wins or loses based on their moves.
- **Restart Option:** Players can restart the game at any time.
